e you have what it takes to be Scooter with your video.<br/> <br/>All tapes submitted to YouTube should include the tag headline: “Guster Scooter For A Day.” All videos also need to be added to the Guster: Scooter For A Day Contest group. The entry deadline is December 10. The winner will be chosen on December 12. The winner will have the following options as a prize:<br/><br/> 1. The winner can choose to go on the cruise with a passenger of their choice if they are both 21+<br/><br/> 2. If the winner is under 21, they can still choose to go on the cruise as long as they are accompanied by someone 25 years or older<br/><br/> 3. Winners under 21, who can not attend the cruise, can also choose to go to a show of their choice (this will include airfare and hotel if need be) <br/> <br/>Good luck!<br/></span>
